{"title":"Nocs Zoom Tube monocular shows a better view of what’s ahead (and right in front of you)","link":"https://bikerumor.com/2021/05/18/nocs-zoom-tube-monocular-shows-a-better-view-of-whats-ahead-and-right-in-front-of-you/","date":1621338775000,"content":"<div id=\"readability-page-1\" class=\"page\"><div><p><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-box-3\"></span>The new NOCS Zoom Tube monocular is a single eye version of <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/2020/12/04/bikerumor-editors-choice-awards-2020-tylers-best-bikes-gear-picks/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">their rugged outdoor binoculars</a>, and it looks like the perfect backcountry adventure tool for scoping the route ahead.</p><p>Like the binoculars, this sporty monocular uses Swiss-designed Bak4 prisms to amplify the image 8x while still having a super short minimum focus distance of just 2m (~7ft). And that’s before we get into the accessories that might make it a life (or tire) saver.</p><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures.jpg\" alt=\"nocs ultralight monoculars for adventure bikepacking and family use\" width=\"1200\" height=\"982\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures-297x243.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures-800x655.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures-120x98.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures-768x628.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures-696x570.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures-1068x874.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures-513x420.jpg 513w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1200px) 100vw, 1200px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures.jpg 1200w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures-297x243.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures-800x655.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures-120x98.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures-768x628.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures-696x570.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures-1068x874.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070835/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-for-backcountry-adventures-513x420.jpg 513w\"></a></p><p>Basic Nocs monocular specs are:<span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-medrectangle-3\"></span></p><ul><li>8×32 (8x magnification x 32mm lens aperture)</li><li>400mm zoom lens equivalent</li><li>Ultrawide field of view (384ft @ 1000 yards / 7.3º)</li><li>IPx6 water resistance</li><li>Scratch-resistant lenses coated to reduce chromatic aberration</li><li>1/4-20 tripod mount</li></ul><p>It also uses their ribbed non-slip surface and an oversized rubbery eyepiece that makes it both comfortable to use and quite durable. It’s small, too, at just 123x68x41mm and weighs in at just 220g. Retail is $75, available in several colors.</p><h2>Nocs Zoom Tube Inspector Microscope</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment.jpg\" alt=\"nocs zoom tube monocular with microscope add on lens for macro views and photos\" width=\"1600\" height=\"653\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-297x121.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-800x327.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-120x49.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-768x313.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-1536x627.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-696x284.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-1068x436.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-1029x420.jpg 1029w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1600px) 100vw, 1600px\" ezimgfmt=\"rs rscb13 src ng ngcb13 srcset\" data-ezsrc=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-297x121.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-800x327.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-120x49.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-768x313.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-1536x627.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-696x284.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-1068x436.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070829/nocs-outdoor-sports-monocular-with-magnifying-lens-attachment-1029x420.jpg 1029w\"></a></p><p>If there were such a thing as a rugged, adventure-ready microscope for the outdoors, this could be it. Add <a href=\"https://www.nocsprovisions.com/collections/accessories/products/inspector-microscope\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Nocs’ Inspector Microscope</a> ($35) attachment and it becomes a 32x power microscope. It’s a 4x power multiplier that refocuses into a macro view of things.</p><p>If you’ve ever needed to see really close to make sure you’re getting all of that thorn out of your tire, or just remove a splinter or read a map’s finer details, here’s your tool. And if you have kids, well, this oughta keep them entertained for a while. They even offer a <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=b5770911-39dc-46ac-ba0f-b49dbb30c5c7&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.backcountry.com%2Fnocs-provisions-photo-rig-binocular-smartphone-adapter&amp;ctc=BRGCOutdoorGeneral\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Photo Rig camera adapter</a> ($27) that lets you turn this into a zoom/macro lens for your smartphone!</p><h2><span data-ez-name=\"bikerumor_com-large-leaderboard-2\"></span>Nocs x Peak Design Capture Kit</h2><p><a href=\"https://s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070841/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-peak-design-capture-kit-strap-mount.jpg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><img loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070841/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-peak-design-capture-kit-strap-mount.jpg\" alt=\"peak design backpack strap mount for nocs monocular and binoculars works the same as their camera mounting system\" width=\"1600\" height=\"765\" data-ezsrcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070841/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-peak-design-capture-kit-strap-mount.jpg 1600w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070841/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-peak-design-capture-kit-strap-mount-297x142.jpg 297w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070841/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-peak-design-capture-kit-strap-mount-800x383.jpg 800w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070841/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-peak-design-capture-kit-strap-mount-1