kit-strap-mount-120x57.jpg 120w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070841/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-peak-design-capture-kit-strap-mount-768x367.jpg 768w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070841/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-peak-design-capture-kit-strap-mount-1536x734.jpg 1536w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070841/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-peak-design-capture-kit-strap-mount-696x333.jpg 696w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070841/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-peak-design-capture-kit-strap-mount-1068x511.jpg 1068w,https://bikerumor.com/ezoimgfmt/s3.amazonaws.com/www.bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2021/05/18070841/nocs-provisions-zoom-tube-monocular-peak-design-capture-kit-strap-mount-878x420.jpg 878w\"></a></p><p>Known for their premium camera mounts, clips, and straps, Peak Design’s <a href=\"https://www.avantlink.com/click.php?tt=el&amp;merchant_id=e295c418-295a-447c-b265-734e25f82503&amp;website_id=3407ca35-0b50-44fe-aeb1-9ab6a93bba54&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.rei.com%2Fproduct%2F132089%2Fpeak-design-capture-30-camera-clip&amp;ctc=BRGCOutdoorGeneral\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">strap-mounted clip ($70)</a> attaches to just about any backpack strap or belt. Then, attach the clip to the Nocs’ 1/4-20 tripod mount and you can stick it directly to your pack’s shoulder straps for easy access.</p><p>It’s the same clip Peak Design sells for cameras, so this kit will work with your DSLR or other cameras and compatible equipment…basically anything with a 1/4-20 mount. Bonus points that the attachment for the monocular has a flat base and can be used as a stand.</p><p><a href=\"https://www.nocsprovisions.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\"><em>NocsProvisions.com</em></a></p></div